{"content": "I need to multiply 471\u2089 \u00d7 340\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n471\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 1\u00d79\u2070 = 4\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 1\u00d71 = 324 + 63 + 1 = 388\u2081\u2080\n\n340\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 0\u00d71 = 243 + 36 + 0 = 279\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n388 \u00d7 279 = 108,252\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n108252 \u00f7 9 = 12028 r 0\n12028 \u00f7 9 = 1336 r 4\n1336 \u00f7 9 = 148 r 4\n148 \u00f7 9 = 16 r 4\n16 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 7\n1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: 174440\u2089\n\n**Verification:**\n174440\u2089 = 1\u00d759049 + 7\u00d76561 + 4\u00d7729 + 4\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 0\u00d71 = 59049 + 45927 + 2916 + 324 + 36 + 0 = 108252\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n174440", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 412}